<Base title="Privacy Policy | ListingDescGen — Real Estate Listing Generator" description="Privacy policy for listing-description-gen.com — how we collect, use, and protect your data.">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto prose prose-lg">
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p><em>Last updated: April 2026</em></p>

    <h2>Who We Are</h2>
    <p>Listing Description Generator ("we", "our") operates listing-description-gen.com — a free tool for generating real estate listing descriptions. Contact: <a href="mailto:privacy@listing-description-gen.com">privacy@listing-description-gen.com</a></p>

    <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
    <p><strong>Tool inputs:</strong> Property details you enter (bedrooms, bathrooms, features, location) are processed in your browser and are not stored on our servers.</p>
    <p><strong>Analytics data:</strong> We use Google Analytics 4 to collect anonymized usage data (pages visited, session duration, general location). This data does not identify you personally.</p>
    <p><strong>Cookies:</strong> Google Analytics sets cookies. Opt out via the <a href="https://tools.google.com/dlpage/gaoptout" rel="noopener noreferrer">Google Analytics opt-out add-on</a>.</p>

    <h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>To understand how visitors use the tool and improve it</li>
      <li>We do not sell, rent, or share personal data with third parties</li>
      <li>Generated listing descriptions belong entirely to you</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Your Rights (GDPR / CCPA)</h2>
    <p>If you are in the EU, UK, or California, you have the right to access, correct, or delete any personal data we hold. Email <a href="mailto:privacy@listing-description-gen.com">privacy@listing-description-gen.com</a> to exercise these rights.</p>

    <h2>Data Retention</h2>
    <p>Analytics data is retained for 14 months. No property data you enter into the tool is retained after your session ends.</p>

    <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
    <p>Material changes will be noted with an updated date above.</p>
  </div>
</Base>
